Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.03,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七话 真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她到底还是发火了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一说我要离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然说「敢走你就走」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说到这个份儿上了还能不走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-宿海?  -你 这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个的话我睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个毛巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个我也睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了能睡好觉下了多少工夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静下来好好想想 你能离家出走几天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说你总不能不去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?这话你也好意思说?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 安城 所谓的学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-只要一次不去就会变得很麻烦的  -诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然最开始的一次很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是休息一天而已并不会有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 因为不会有什么变化就日复一日 日复一日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样积累下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等发觉的时候自己已经完全...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 我都不配说这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海你真厉害 没有白当家里蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-果然 宿海没变  -嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己最困难的时候 也总是为别人着想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别太过分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是像这样顾这个顾那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有呢 要说也该去说面码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我和雪集也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们总是活在面码的阴影之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会不会不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这么说 她现在就在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以说 这种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信面码的事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说我不信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:01:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了牛肉咖喱来 anaru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百二十元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉咖喱撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来看日记的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的牛肉咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过这个之后或许就能知道面码的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有我所不了解的面码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不了解的面码的情感 就在这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(今天和大家一起去玩了 非常有趣)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(今天和大家一起去玩了 非常开心)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好随意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有趣就是开心 只有这点差别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不擅长作文呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个有些不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩的时候摔倒了 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 这里也不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起到仁太的妈妈那里探病去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来以前经常去呢 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太的妈妈一直在住院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我们给神写信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请神让仁太的妈妈快点好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么给?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.78,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(龙势就是火箭花火 个头很大)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家决定一起来做花火 我想应该会很难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想起来了 把信装在火箭花火里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后发给神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 愿望会不会就是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一定是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候本来想做的结果没做成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我妈妈...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管什么仁太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜吃东西可是会变成猪的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要变成猪的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 盐拉面 加蛋花的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为找不到阿权拉面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂你点吃的让你心情好点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸差不多要回来了 快点吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我明天也会去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说...别跟我一起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奖励 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不能再做奇怪的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 为什么你没去学校还穿着校服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有什么关系啊 所谓的时尚就是自由  -不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火药管理法规定 要使用花火用的火药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要十八岁以上拥有国家资格才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是玩具花火之类的话似乎还可以搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也需要有执照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 仔细想想做花火是要资格的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说起来 昨天打扫的时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜集大量的花火 把火药全部取出来集中到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把火药包进厕纸芯里 会燃起来所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不废话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕 小鬼好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 以前认为这是可行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就算这种东西 也觉得它一定能飞起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得我们能做出比花火大会看到的飞的还要高的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生看起来已经完全是大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好像什么都能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真正觉得什么都能做到的 其实是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先确定个可以实现的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这么说 应该没希望的吧 无论怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做再多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你所说的面码的愿望的话 就只是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 宿海君 你有好好向你家的面码确认过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许 或许我是害怕向她本人确认吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一瞬感觉似曾相识  -诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直走在前面的宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在背后望着他的可怜的雪集君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 为什么你不说出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是他说要到秘密基地集合...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天...好像是面码提出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对 是面码打电话叫我出来...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 那天 她好像说有什么事想商量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易想起来了 为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为宿海在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了一件重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大家不要告诉宿海 面码那天说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?面码说的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火?我认识会做的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我工地的一个大叔在祭典的时候是花火师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么仁太 想做花火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?啊...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊...就是想做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人做?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 和波波他们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么 这样啊 那我帮你跟他说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 仁太 仁太 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走不出孔达鲁町了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.89,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你联系一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事回头再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单的也需要这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要做都还是能做得出的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十万?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...我都没见过二十万长什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 一定能凑齐的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我和anaru拼命打工的话 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你能不能不要擅自做主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好嘛 互相帮助嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 只要anaru一周七天全打工绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 我还没同意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.01,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也...打工...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也参加!打工!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里输入金额记住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是中古品的价格 这边是新品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 然后在这里输入差额啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我花了一个月才掌握的技巧你怎么一来就会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你花太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你就完全不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 果然是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-打工倒没请假啊  -学校就没去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 看啊 那不是不来学校的那小子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 这两个家伙有一腿?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 艳福不浅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎!!!光临!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子傻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干 干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样和你在一起 感觉和小时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下胶带 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 宿...海...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 anaru
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不许叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海打工啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火的事 看来是认真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么着 咱们也凑点钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给宿海去胡闹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不参与的话 我也就不参与了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 出来坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快考试了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是年级第四
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年级第二居然说这种话...再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪着你可是相当累人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 这么晚...不良少年!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太绝对不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上睡这么早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.56,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上走这么早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天狗狗的小节目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的狗如果是母的 仁太肯定在做什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小狗叫奥斯卡鲁 雌性 七岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 八哥好可爱 褶子真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是母的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在这名簿上签字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 仁太君退学了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?没啊 不过 为什么这样问呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 问这种奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 前两天 看到他好像在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太君 这些事都告诉爸爸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我家是自由意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事都是仁太自己做决定 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事!有事有事有事有事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 波波?嗯 今天没有我的班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长好像很欣赏他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上和他一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:17:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 羊山的工地?!这活儿太重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 要挣钱还是体力劳动最快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭花火 钱也都要飞走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望...面码的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想想你自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人替你着急啊 这种态度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 雪集他们最近有联络过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 偶尔有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也来多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么放心不下仁太的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 仁太就是仁太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一直叫仁太的吗 我叫仁太怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人!这边!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄完了来这边!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子好拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 很帅啊 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码没有为自己着想的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太一直在为面码着想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 当心脚下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自改变灯的朝向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风能吹得动灯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊 闪闪发光的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么吃得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好吃!  -真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和老妈做的味道差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁太 学校辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 不过很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么说呢 比总是呆在家里要轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种活着的实在感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 不是说那个活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一直 怎么说呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码看到有活着的实在感的仁太 也感觉活着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我把定金先拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能还差很多 不过这样可以先开始做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 不好意思 这事不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心跟祭典的干事说走嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他就生气说我居然帮高中生做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这么拼命地赚钱...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊 那个干事 我直接去找他谈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...本间家的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码家的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太君他们好像在为你做各种努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑啊